 the academic rigors associated with most state colleges  As the Commandant of Cadets  I am responsible for the daily military regimen that sets this college apart  Whether in the Barracks  on the parade ground or on the athletic fields  it is my mission to continuously create challenging leadership and training experiences that reinforce cadet success while working through VMI s developmental systems  VMI prepares cadets to be whatever they resolve to be  The challenges encourage the development of the total person for success at VMI and in life  The individual growth over the four year journey distinguishes VMI graduates from those of other colleges and universities It s a tough journey but one well worth taking  Colonel William Wanovich VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 